query:
SELECT 
  se.id, 
  se.title, 
  se.subjectId,
  sub.name as subject_name,
  sub.code as subject_code,
  se.availableFrom,
  se.availableTo,
  se.status,
  se.totalQuestions,
  se.totalPoints,
  se.createdAt
FROM student_exercises se
JOIN subjects sub ON se.subjectId = sub.id
ORDER BY se.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
